{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011h4EFHYq7hXSDfYh1wy4HM","type":"tool_result","content":"292-### Merge & Validation\n293-\n294:- FR12: System can merge an epic's branch into main after epic completion\n295:- FR13: System can detect merge conflicts from failed `git merge`\n296-- FR14: System can dispatch a merge agent with conflict context from both branches\n297-- FR15: System can run the full test suite on the merged result before accepting\n298:- FR16: System can reject a merge and escalate to the user if tests fail after conflict resolution\n299:- FR17: User can configure merge strategy (rebase or merge-commit)\n300-\n301-### Engine-Handled Tasks\n--\n337-- NFR2: Multi-lane TUI must render at 15 FPS with up to 4 concurrent lanes\n338-- NFR3: Telemetry NDJSON write must complete within 10ms per entry\n339:- NFR4: Merge operation (non-conflicting) must complete within 30 seconds\n340-- NFR5: Cross-worktree test suite must complete within the project's normal test timeout\n341-\n--\n351-\n352-- NFR11: Git worktree commands must work with the project's existing git hooks\n353:- NFR12: Worktree branches must not conflict with user's existing branches (prefix with `codeharness/`)\n354:- NFR13: Telemetry NDJSON format must be stable across versions (versioned entries)"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_012CEScWqqGFCq4Y2DMk4BYh","session_id":"80ecde4e-3ccc-44de-925d-a2036bf845d1","uuid":"6046ef7d-1808-44e1-8518-8acdba613dc3","timestamp":"2026-04-03T21:15:32.261Z"}
